data.value: . TO ENCRYPT A MESSAGE, you have to generate a key first. . TO GENERATE A KEY, press the set key button. . Click the generate key button to generate an encryption key. Use the back button on the top left to go back to the main menu. . Press the encrypt button to enter the encrypt area. . Enter the text that you want to encrypt and press the encrypt button present below the box. . Click the back button top left to leave the encrypting area. . TO DECRYPT A MESSAGE, press the decrypt button. . Enter the key that was used to encrypt the message in the text box near the top. . Enter the message that you want to decrypt in the text box present at the bottom and press the decrypt button present below the box. . Click the back button top left to leave the decrypting area. . TO SAVE YOUR PASSWORDS, press the password button. . Enter the app name, username and password that you want to save.
